OL,3,CHero neighbours save family from fire
OL,5,FA group of neighbours have been
OL,6,Fpraised for banding together and
OL,7,Frescuing a family of three from a
OL,8,Fhouse fire.
OL,10,FSharon Henrys raised the alarm when
OL,11,Fshe heard screams for help coming from
OL,12,Fthe street, in Leigh, around 6am on 18
OL,13,FDecember.
OL,15,FShe had been making coffee and
OL,16,Fimmediately abandoned her task to
OL,17,Fknock on the doors and windows of
OL,18,Fsurrounding houses for help.
