OL,3,CHero neighbours save family from fire
OL,5,F"When I looked out the window I saw
OL,6,Fkids hanging from their window and
OL,7,Ftheir dad shouting for help," Sharon
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"I came flying down and started really
OL,11,Fshouting in the street. That's when
OL,12,FRay came flying out."
OL,14,FRay Cross heard her calls and ran
OL,15,Foutside in his pyjamas before grabbing
OL,16,Fhold of a ladder from his front yard
OL,17,Fand usinf it to save the dad and one
OL,18,Fof his daughters.
OL,20,F"When I got the ladder, they were all
OL,21,Fperched on the window ledge.
