OL,3,CHero neighbours save family from fire
OL,5,F"I went up, got one girl, come down,
OL,6,Fwent up again, the dad was there but I
OL,7,Fcouldn't reach the other girl," Ray
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FThe other daughter was stuck in the
OL,11,Fengulfed house, and a third neighbour,
OL,12,FBen Hughes, ran to help.
OL,14,FAs he stood beneath the window, the
OL,15,Fgirl jumped, and Ben caught her.
OL,17,F"She's the hero for jumping," Ben
OL,18,Fsaid. "She was really hesitant and
OL,19,Fbecause Ray screamed 'jump' she jumped
OL,20,Finto my arms.
