OL,3,CHero neighbours save family from fire
OL,5,F"I'm still wired up from it, from how
OL,6,Fit all happened. We all stick together
OL,7,Faround here."
OL,9,FNeighbours say the blaze on Laxey
OL,10,FCrescent started at the back of the
OL,11,Fsemi-detached house before quickly
OL,12,Fspreading.
OL,14,FNeighbour Jody Shovelton has set up an
OL,15,Fonline fundraiser to help the family,
OL,16,Fwhich has already raised #8,000. The
OL,17,Ffundraiser says: "In a matter of
OL,18,Fmoments, they lost their home and
OL,19,Feverything they own."
