OL,3,CHero neighbours save family from fire
OL,5,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,6,Fsaid in a statement: "The family were
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital as a precaution but
OL,8,Fthankfully it is not thought their
OL,9,Finjuries are serious, due to the fast
OL,10,Fwork of their neighbours."
OL,12,FFour fire engines attended the scene.
OL,13,FChris Evans, the station manager for
OL,14,FWigan and Hindley fire station said:
OL,15,F"What the neighbours did here in
OL,16,Fhelping to rescue this family was
OL,17,Fincredibly brave and we commend them
OL,18,Ffor this."
OL,20,FAn investigation into the cause of the
OL,21,Ffire is ongoing.
